471
01:14:42,040 --> 01:14:45,220
 imam situaciju, ovako, imam to.

472
01:14:45,220 --> 01:14:51,480
 I onda dobiješ ono, tipa, moram kontrolirati svoju prvu reakciju

473
01:14:51,480 --> 01:14:54,040
 i kada sam to učinio u danu.

474
01:14:54,040 --> 01:14:57,160
 I to svaku, nakon večere se te obaveze ispunje.

475
01:14:57,160 --> 01:14:58,020
 Znači, vrlo mjerljivo.

476
01:14:58,020 --> 01:14:58,400
 Da.

477
01:14:58,400 --> 01:14:59,040
 Da, da.

478
01:14:59,040 --> 01:15:03,600
 Kad si bio, ovaj, negdje prvi,

479
01:15:03,640 --> 01:15:08,240
 kad si nekome otišao u susred reč da čini krivo,

480
01:15:08,240 --> 01:15:11,260
 to je po meni najteže, jel, nekog u korit.

481
01:15:11,260 --> 01:15:15,840
 To jest, znači, taj Elvira je nama uvijek pričala

482
01:15:15,840 --> 01:15:17,900
 grijeh propusta je najveći grijeh.

483
01:15:17,900 --> 01:15:20,440
 Kad vidiš da neko radi krivo, ti prođeš pored njega.

484
01:15:20,440 --> 01:15:24,320
 Znači, i ne opamjeneš ga da, ono, radi krivo.

485
01:15:24,320 --> 01:15:25,780
 znači činiš grijeh propusta.

486
01:15:25,780 --> 01:15:29,500
 I tu je ona jako, jako je to strogo napravljeno.

487
01:15:29,500 --> 01:15:32,800
 I to je, ono, super je to meni, meni bilo.

488
01:15:32,800 --> 01:15:35,420
 Ali, evo, jako je, opet dajemu reći...

489
01:15:35,420 --> 01:15:36,840
 Ti je mijao ljudima oko tebe nije.

490
01:15:36,840 --> 01:15:38,820
 A nije ni meni, znači, nije, nije.

491
01:15:38,820 --> 01:15:41,320
 Bilo je teško otići, znači, jako je teško otići

492
01:15:41,320 --> 01:15:45,940
 u susred nekom i reći, ono, ej, radiš krivo

493
01:15:45,940 --> 01:15:48,000
 ili kako se to ponašaš ili kako to...

494
01:15:48,000 --> 01:15:50,600
 A lakše bi to u stvari primio od nekoga neg da...

495
01:15:50,600 --> 01:15:51,320
 Tako, nego reći.

496
01:15:51,320 --> 01:15:54,560
 I onda, znači, zavisi i od dana

497
01:15:54,560 --> 01:15:59,560
 i radni dan završava u 6-7.

498
01:15:59,560 --> 01:16:05,000
 Oko 7, pola 8 je večera.

499
01:16:05,000 --> 01:16:07,780
 Prije toga nekako, ono, krunica.

500
01:16:09,180 --> 01:16:13,760
 Ima jutarnja krunica, onda ima krunica

501
01:16:13,760 --> 01:16:18,080
 na radnom mjestu, dok traje radno...

502
01:16:18,080 --> 01:16:21,740
 Tepo, popadon, popodneni radni dio.

503
01:16:21,740 --> 01:16:25,860
 I onda ima zadnja krunica,

504
01:16:25,860 --> 01:16:30,120
 da li je ona šetajuća prije večere

505
01:16:30,120 --> 01:16:33,080
 ili je u kapeli nakon večere,

506
01:16:33,080 --> 01:16:38,340
 pa je još neki, ono, neka duhovna, ono, tema.

507
01:16:39,180 --> 01:16:45,160
 To je to i u 9.30 ide u sobe

508
01:16:45,160 --> 01:16:47,240
 i u 10.00 se ga svijetla i spasa.

509
01:16:47,240 --> 01:16:52,620
 Dobro, a kaj je ako se neko neće dići ujutro u 15.00 do 6.00?

510
01:16:52,620 --> 01:16:55,420
 Ja odlučim, ja odlučimo se spavati.

511
01:16:57,140 --> 01:16:59,680
 Mora se digniti, ne može ne digniti se.

512
01:16:59,680 --> 01:17:00,640
 Neko te digne.

513
01:17:00,640 --> 01:17:03,120
 Ti ne moraš ići

514
01:17:03,120 --> 01:17:04,760
 moliti krunicu,

515
01:17:04,760 --> 01:17:07,420
 ali ideš raditi odmah u 15.00 do 6.00

516
01:17:07,420 --> 01:17:08,120
 i to je to.

517
01:17:08,120 --> 01:17:09,960
 Ali se moraš digniti.

518
01:17:09,960 --> 01:17:12,220
 Ok, sad kad se rekao ne moraš moliti krunicu,

519
01:17:12,220 --> 01:17:14,060
 je li uvijed za uću čenakolo,

520
01:17:14,060 --> 01:17:16,520
 poprosti, kje opće znači čenakolo?

521
01:17:16,520 --> 01:17:18,780
 Čenakolo je dvorana posljednje večere,

522
01:17:18,780 --> 01:17:24,460
 ili tamo gdje su se apostoli sakrili

523
01:17:24,460 --> 01:17:27,240
 dok nije došao do sveti.

524
01:17:27,240 --> 01:17:32,040
 Je li nekakav uvijed za uću čenakolo da si vijednik?

525
01:17:32,040 --> 01:17:34,500
 Može ući bilo ko.

526
01:17:34,500 --> 01:17:36,960
 Bilo ko ima potrebu,

527
01:17:36,960 --> 01:17:38,440
 može ući čenakolo bez obzira.

528
01:17:38,440 --> 01:17:40,440
 Ja sam u...

529
01:17:40,440 --> 01:17:43,920
 Ok, bilo je puno priča,

530
01:17:43,920 --> 01:17:46,700
 znači i islamske vjeroispovijesti,

531
01:17:47,000 --> 01:17:50,320
 protestantske vjeroispovijesti

532
01:17:50,320 --> 01:17:54,920
 i ortodoksne...

533
01:17:54,920 --> 01:17:55,540
 Pravoslavaca.

534
01:17:55,540 --> 01:17:57,460
 Pravoslavaca, Makedonaca.

535
01:17:57,460 --> 01:17:58,860
 Ali oni kao isto isprate normalno

536
01:17:58,860 --> 01:17:59,980
 sada taj program ili...

537
01:17:59,980 --> 01:18:00,140
 Da.

538
01:18:00,140 --> 01:18:00,940
 Da, ok.

539
01:18:00,940 --> 01:18:02,720
 I ja sam, evo,

540
01:18:02,720 --> 01:18:05,220
 konkretno doživio neka, ono,

541
01:18:05,220 --> 01:18:11,220
 obraćenja sa islama na katoličanstvo

542
01:18:11,220 --> 01:18:13,220
 i cijelih obitelji.

543
01:18:13,220 --> 01:18:16,220
 Ono, pogotovo ljudi,

544
01:18:17,000 --> 01:18:17,760
 u Kosovo.

545
01:18:17,760 --> 01:18:22,520
 Moj jako dobar prijatelj je, ono,

546
01:18:22,520 --> 01:18:25,080
 se obratio, krstio,

547
01:18:25,080 --> 01:18:27,540
 pričestio krizmo,

548
01:18:27,540 --> 01:18:28,880
 njegovi roditelji

549
01:18:28,880 --> 01:18:32,360
 i danas ti ljudi vode

550
01:18:32,360 --> 01:18:34,180
 zajednicu u Prištini.

551
01:18:34,180 --> 01:18:36,160
 Dobro, znači,

552
01:18:36,160 --> 01:18:37,240
 nije uvijek zavuć

553
01:18:37,240 --> 01:18:39,540
 ko vjernik,

554
01:18:39,540 --> 01:18:41,980
 a, jel ima puno ljudi

555
01:18:41,980 --> 01:18:43,720
 koji izađuju iz černako,

556
01:18:43,720 --> 01:18:46,060
 ali nisu vjernici ili...

557
01:18:46,060 --> 01:18:46,400
 Supra.

558
01:18:50,000 --> 01:18:51,140
 Zakaj to pitam.

559
01:18:51,140 --> 01:18:54,780
 Vidim da je, u stvari,

560
01:18:54,780 --> 01:18:56,580
 jako prožito po danu,

561
01:18:56,580 --> 01:18:59,020
 znači, ta jedan fizički rad

562
01:18:59,020 --> 01:19:02,120
 i duhovna ta komponenta.

563
01:19:02,120 --> 01:19:05,620
 Je li može jedna bez druge,

564
01:19:05,620 --> 01:19:06,740
 ili bi mogo reći,

565
01:19:06,740 --> 01:19:08,780
 koja je važnija u tom procesu

566
01:19:08,780 --> 01:19:11,200
 koji tamo dečki prolaze?

567
01:19:11,700 --> 01:19:13,880
 Pa, ne može jedna bez druge,

568
01:19:13,880 --> 01:19:15,560
 a važnija je duhovna.

569
01:19:15,560 --> 01:19:17,280
 I na tome je, ono,

570
01:19:17,280 --> 01:19:21,200
 cijeli sukus je na duhovnost.

571
01:19:21,200 --> 01:19:22,260
 Kak bi mi to argumentirao?

572
01:19:22,260 --> 01:19:22,880
 Zašto duhovno?

573
01:19:22,880 --> 01:19:27,720
 Pa, zato što se uvijek ideš,

574
01:19:27,720 --> 01:19:31,120
 znači, ljubi bližnjeg svog

575
01:19:31,120 --> 01:19:32,120
 kao samog sebe,

576
01:19:32,120 --> 01:19:36,260
 ono, samaritanac,

577
01:19:40,580 --> 01:19:44,200
 tipa vjera te tvoja spasla,

578
01:19:44,200 --> 01:19:46,880
 to su neke stvari

579
01:19:46,880 --> 01:19:48,480
 koje zajednica

580
01:19:48,480 --> 01:19:50,640
 najviše gleda

581
01:19:50,640 --> 01:19:51,360
 i u tome

582
01:19:51,360 --> 01:19:53,480
 najveću

583
01:19:53,480 --> 01:19:55,080
 i, ajmo reći, pažnju

584
01:19:55,080 --> 01:19:56,720
 daje tome.

585
01:19:56,720 --> 01:19:58,120
 Znači, fizički rad

586
01:19:58,120 --> 01:20:00,160
 je bitan

587
01:20:00,160 --> 01:20:03,080
 i rad je sam po sebi dar

588
01:20:03,080 --> 01:20:05,640
 i, mislim,

589
01:20:05,640 --> 01:20:07,100
 mora ga biti,

590
01:20:07,100 --> 01:20:08,200
 ali da bi mogao

591
01:20:08,200 --> 01:20:09,880
 živjeti,

592
01:20:10,000 --> 01:20:11,420
 ali, ono,

593
01:20:11,420 --> 01:20:13,120
 Elvira je uvijek

594
01:20:13,120 --> 01:20:15,300
 nas poticala

595
01:20:15,300 --> 01:20:17,620
 da nikada ne

596
01:20:17,620 --> 01:20:18,820
 bježimo

597
01:20:18,820 --> 01:20:20,260
 i ne skrivamo se

598
01:20:20,260 --> 01:20:21,320
 iza posla, jel?

599
01:20:21,320 --> 01:20:22,840
 Znači, da se treba

600
01:20:22,840 --> 01:20:24,680
 suočiti sa sobom,

601
01:20:24,680 --> 01:20:25,320
 s Bogom,

602
01:20:25,320 --> 01:20:26,800
 treba se Hrvat s Bogom

603
01:20:26,800 --> 01:20:28,160
 ono,

604
01:20:28,160 --> 01:20:31,100
 pričat s njim jednostavno,

605
01:20:31,100 --> 01:20:32,060
 iako ti ne ide

606
01:20:32,060 --> 01:20:33,260
 i teško ti je, ono,

607
01:20:33,260 --> 01:20:34,480
 znaš, da ti imaš s njim

608
01:20:34,480 --> 01:20:36,000
 neki dijalog, ono,

609
01:20:36,000 --> 01:20:37,280
 zašto, zbog čega,

610
01:20:37,540 --> 01:20:38,960
 da se imaš pravo se naljutiti

611
01:20:38,960 --> 01:20:39,220
 na nje,

612
01:20:39,220 --> 01:20:40,960
 onaj, to je naš, ono,

613
01:20:40,960 --> 01:20:42,460
 slobodno se naljutiti.

614
01:20:42,460 --> 01:20:45,520
 finno rukavicama,

615
01:20:45,520 --> 01:20:46,840
 pobožne molitve,

616
01:20:46,840 --> 01:20:49,720
 di ti naučene molitve,

617
01:20:49,720 --> 01:20:50,220
 tak neke.

618
01:20:50,220 --> 01:20:51,180
 Cilje je kagod,

619
01:20:51,180 --> 01:20:52,380
 znači, rukama i nogama.

620
01:20:52,380 --> 01:20:53,320
 Rukama i nogama,

621
01:20:53,320 --> 01:20:54,420
 samo da, ono,

622
01:20:54,420 --> 01:20:56,860
 da dođeš do tog trenutka

623
01:20:56,860 --> 01:20:57,680
 da osjetiš to.

624
01:20:57,680 --> 01:20:58,340
 Nije bitno,

625
01:20:58,340 --> 01:20:59,260
 ono, na koji način.

626
01:20:59,740 --> 01:21:01,080
 znači, imaš način,

627
01:21:01,080 --> 01:21:04,480
 alat krunica

628
01:21:04,480 --> 01:21:06,120
 i misa.

629
01:21:06,120 --> 01:21:08,700
 I to je to,

630
01:21:08,700 --> 01:21:10,000
 imaš sve to pismo

631
01:21:10,000 --> 01:21:10,740
 i,

632
01:21:10,740 --> 01:21:12,460
 znaš,

633
01:21:12,460 --> 01:21:14,000
 kako ti to hoćeš,

634
01:21:14,000 --> 01:21:15,080
 tako ti to, ono.

635
01:21:15,080 --> 01:21:17,240
 A, kaj bi sad ti meni rekao da

636
01:21:17,240 --> 01:21:20,360
 tu nas pro tebe sedje neko ko kaže,

637
01:21:20,360 --> 01:21:22,360
 ok, ja konzumiram drogu

638
01:21:22,360 --> 01:21:23,740
 već dugi niz godina,

639
01:21:24,500 --> 01:21:25,100
 međutim,

640
01:21:25,100 --> 01:21:27,280
 ja sam isto tako,

641
01:21:27,280 --> 01:21:27,780
 vjernik,

642
01:21:27,780 --> 01:21:28,680
 ovoga,

643
01:21:28,680 --> 01:21:30,260
 nebitno obratio,

644
01:21:30,260 --> 01:21:31,020
 ne obratio kagod,

645
01:21:31,020 --> 01:21:31,320
 opće,

646
01:21:31,320 --> 01:21:32,120
 ne, ne, ne,

647
01:21:32,120 --> 01:21:34,380
 čak neću reći da podrazumijem

648
01:21:34,380 --> 01:21:35,540
 da vjernik nema problem s drogom,

649
01:21:35,540 --> 01:21:36,620
 znači, to je jednostavno neka stvar

650
01:21:36,620 --> 01:21:37,480
 u koju možeš upasni,

651
01:21:37,480 --> 01:21:38,520
 opće,

652
01:21:38,520 --> 01:21:39,600
 ne,

653
01:21:39,600 --> 01:21:41,360
 ne želim čak reći da si loša osoba,

654
01:21:41,360 --> 01:21:41,900
 nego jednostavno,

655
01:21:41,900 --> 01:21:42,720
 ok, imaš takav,

656
01:21:42,720 --> 01:21:46,360
 tak se dogodilo.

657
01:21:46,360 --> 01:21:47,880
 I ja,

658
01:21:47,880 --> 01:21:50,260
 i osoba preko puta tebe,

659
01:21:50,260 --> 01:21:51,300
 u ovom slučaju ja kaže,

660
01:21:51,300 --> 01:21:51,560
 ok,

661
01:21:51,560 --> 01:21:54,340
 ja ne bi ušao

662
01:21:54,340 --> 01:21:55,840
 u zajednicu,

663
01:21:55,840 --> 01:21:57,680
 ja ću se samo,

664
01:21:57,680 --> 01:21:59,600
 još ja će molit Bogu.

665
01:21:59,600 --> 01:22:04,100
 To je apsolutno njegovo pravo.

666
01:22:04,100 --> 01:22:07,020
 A kad bi te ja tražio

667
01:22:07,020 --> 01:22:08,680
 tvoje mišljenje na tu moju tezu?

668
01:22:08,680 --> 01:22:11,120
 Pa gledaj,

669
01:22:11,120 --> 01:22:11,420
 ja,

670
01:22:11,420 --> 01:22:14,860
 mislim da molitva sigurno može pomoć,

671
01:22:14,860 --> 01:22:16,280
 apsolutno,

672
01:22:16,280 --> 01:22:18,320
 ili pomogla meni,

673
01:22:18,320 --> 01:22:22,440
 taj odnos s Bogom sigurno može pomoć,

674
01:22:22,440 --> 01:22:23,460
 ili pomogla meni,

675
01:22:24,180 --> 01:22:26,800
 možda mi je više pomogao nego odnos sa

676
01:22:26,800 --> 01:22:31,280
 mojim bližnjima.

677
01:22:31,280 --> 01:22:37,420
 Taj odnos i ta molitva mi je ono,

678
01:22:37,420 --> 01:22:39,060
 kako bi rekao,

679
01:22:39,060 --> 01:22:39,520
 otvorila oči,

680
01:22:39,520 --> 01:22:43,520
 potakla me na neka promišljenja,

681
01:22:45,520 --> 01:22:49,480
 nužno nije da ti moraš biti u ono,

682
01:22:49,480 --> 01:22:49,980
 kako bi rekao,

683
01:22:49,980 --> 01:22:52,300
 zatvoren u zajednici

684
01:22:52,300 --> 01:22:57,140
 i da se bez toga ne možeš riješiti.

685
01:22:57,140 --> 01:22:58,960
 Ja samo kažem da je ono,

686
01:22:58,960 --> 01:23:01,420
 gdje su dvoje i troje u moj ime,

687
01:23:01,420 --> 01:23:03,620
 tu sam ja s njima ide puno lakše,

688
01:23:03,620 --> 01:23:06,640
 jer sam je jako teško,

689
01:23:07,640 --> 01:23:08,260
 ali ono,

690
01:23:08,260 --> 01:23:09,500
 s Bogom nisi sam,

691
01:23:09,500 --> 01:23:10,540
 pa ono,

692
01:23:10,540 --> 01:23:13,200
 apsolutno podržavam,

693
01:23:13,200 --> 01:23:17,000
 ali po meni da je lakše

694
01:23:17,000 --> 01:23:18,300
 i da je možda

695
01:23:18,300 --> 01:23:20,980
 jednostavnije,

696
01:23:20,980 --> 01:23:22,340
 pragmatičnije,

697
01:23:22,340 --> 01:23:24,440
 neću reći brže,

698
01:23:24,640 --> 01:23:27,840
 ali u nekom kontekstu

699
01:23:27,840 --> 01:23:30,660
 je sigurno da smo ono,

700
01:23:30,660 --> 01:23:32,600
 da si u...

701
01:23:32,600 --> 01:23:33,840
 A to je neki u tabani put,

702
01:23:33,840 --> 01:23:34,500
 bih rekli u stvari,

703
01:23:34,500 --> 01:23:35,800
 da si s nekim

704
01:23:35,800 --> 01:23:36,480
 i da ti on,

705
01:23:36,480 --> 01:23:38,060
 znaš,

706
01:23:38,060 --> 01:23:40,480
 da te vodi,

707
01:23:40,480 --> 01:23:41,640
 znači da ti kaže

708
01:23:41,640 --> 01:23:42,720
 nemoj ići tu desno,

709
01:23:42,720 --> 01:23:43,240
 idi ljevo,

710
01:23:43,240 --> 01:23:44,260
 znači da ti ta ruku

711
01:23:44,260 --> 01:23:46,820
 kroz šumu

712
01:23:46,820 --> 01:23:47,640
 da te provede,

713
01:23:47,640 --> 01:23:48,320
 mi ono,

714
01:23:48,320 --> 01:23:48,800
 znaš,

715
01:23:48,800 --> 01:23:51,040
 dosta puta ti ne vidiš

716
01:23:51,040 --> 01:23:53,300
 drva od šume,

717
01:23:53,300 --> 01:23:53,880
 znači,

718
01:23:53,880 --> 01:23:55,300
 ili ono,

719
01:23:55,300 --> 01:23:57,400
 da jednostavno ti neko da,

720
01:23:57,400 --> 01:24:00,000
 da ti bude to neko svjetlo

721
01:24:00,000 --> 01:24:02,020
 i da te ono vodi,

722
01:24:02,020 --> 01:24:02,960
 znači ali,

723
01:24:02,960 --> 01:24:04,720
 da li čovjek može

724
01:24:04,720 --> 01:24:06,380
 se riješiti toga sam,

725
01:24:06,380 --> 01:24:07,700
 može,

726
01:24:07,700 --> 01:24:09,280
 ja vjerujem da može.

727
01:24:09,280 --> 01:24:10,520
